description: Simris Alg AB is engaged in the development and production of health products and supplements from farmed algae. The firm operates as a manufacturer of dietary supplements and specialty foods. The firm's products are based on algae-plants that live in water, such as seaweed, phytoplankton and kelp. These products are rich of Omega-3 oils and made from natural ingredients. The firm offers a wide range of algae-based supplements and foods, among them are Simris Algae Omega-3 Original, Simris Algae Omega-3 for Mothers, Simris Algae Omega-3 for Athletes, Finest Chlorella, Sundried Spirulina, Boosting Astaxanthin, Chlorella Crispies, Flower Power Algae Tea, Sun Candy Algae Tea and other.
name: Simris Alg AB
